1. *Bolesno* je koliko mnogo novca trošim na cigarete. (Sickening is how much money I spend on cigarettes.) 
2. Koliko puta da ti kažem da mi *bolesno* ideš na živce? (How many times do I have to tell you that you *sicken* me?)
3. Ne znam kako možeš da slušaš tu *bolesnu* muziku. (I don't know how you can listen to that *sick* music.)
4. Ovaj grad je *bolesno* gužvan uveče. (This city is *sickeningly* crowded at night.)
5. Tvoje ponašanje mi se čini *bolesnim*. (Your behavior seems *sick* to me.)
6. Oni ljudi su *bolesni* ako misle da mogu da uspeju bez truda. (Those people are *sick* if they think they can succeed without effort.)
7. Njegova opsesija za čistoćom je *bolesna*. (His obsession with cleanliness is *sickening*.)
8. *Bolesno* je koliko ljudi u današnje vreme ne poštuju osnovna pravila ponašanja. (It's *sickening* how many people nowadays don't respect basic rules of conduct.)